description:
2 BEDS + OFFICE w VIEWS! IMMEDIATE OCCUPANCY! The Residences at 232 Old Colony are located in Boston's fastest growing and most desirable neighborhood South Boston. This elevator building offers contemporary design finishes, featuring hardwood floors throughout, stainless steel Jenn Air appliances, gas cooking, a state of the art in-home sound system. Right across from the Washington Village development, and only 0.3 miles to the Red Line! Direct access garage parking available!

Perks:
1500+ sqft
Heat, Gas, Water included!
Pets allowed!
Keyless entry 
Garage Parking x 1
Nest smart thermostat
Master Bedroom Projector
In-home sound system 
Bed Frame & Mattress included

Owner pays water, heat, and gas. 
Tenant pays cable, internet, and electricity
